snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 – Homelander vs. Omni-Man Trailer
snippet.description:
Planes, trains, and an earth-shattering rivalry. Homelander and Omni-Man finally square off for the fight of their lives.

Get the Premium Edition or the Kombat Pack to play these characters: https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase 
- Play as Homelander now in Early Access, full release June 11!
- Play as Omni-Man now!

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
